metadata.title: Miscellaneous Lines (airstrips) - CNF

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Infrastructure;   Miscellaneous lines - airstrips with name and type in Chugach National Forest. The coverage of the Big Islands Management Area currently contains float plane strips. Scale is 1:31,680 and 1:63,360.
